    "reviews": [
      {
        "text": "I found this place through Google reviews and, as someone from India who doesn’t speak great Spanish, I was struggling to find a reliable shop to fix my car after an accident. César was fantastic—professional, helpful, and honest. The price was reasonable, and most importantly, the job was completed within the promised timeframe. Highly recommend!",
